---
/**
 * Full homepage layout for Particulieren, inspired by Rabobank design.
 * Provides hero, product cards, and content sections when CMS content areas are empty.
 */
---

<!-- ============================== -->
<!-- HERO SECTION                   -->
<!-- ============================== -->
<section class="relative flex w-full items-center min-h-[500px] md:min-h-[600px] overflow-hidden">
    <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1529156069898-49953e39b3ac?w=1600&h=700&fit=crop&crop=faces"
        alt="Familie samen"
        class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover"
        loading="eager"
        width="1600"
        height="700"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-neutral/80 via-neutral/50 to-transparent"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20 py-16 max-w-screen-xl mx-auto w-full">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Particulieren</h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80 max-w-lg mb-8">
            Welkom bij Rabobank. Van betalen tot hypotheek, wij helpen je met al je financiele zaken.
        </p>
        <a href="#content" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Ontdek meer</a>
    </div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 z-10">
        <a href="#content">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white/60 animate-bounce" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
            </svg>
        </a>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================== -->
<!-- INTRO TEXT                      -->
<!-- ============================== -->
<section id="content" class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-6 py-10 md:py-14">
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-3xl text-base-content/80">
        <p>
            Bij Rabobank kun je terecht voor al je bankzaken. Of je nu een rekening wilt openen,
            wilt sparen, beleggen of een hypotheek nodig hebt — wij staan voor je klaar met
            persoonlijk advies en digitale oplossingen.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================== -->
<!-- PRODUCT CARDS GRID              -->
<!-- ============================== -->
<section class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-6 pb-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <!-- Betalen -->
        <a href="/betalen/" class="bg-primary text-primary-content rounded-xl p-6 pb-10 relative group hover:brightness-110 transition-all duration-300 min-h-[160px] flex flex-col justify-between" data-aos="fade-up">
            <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold italic mb-2">Betalen</h3>
                <p class="text-sm opacity-80">Kies de betaalrekening die bij je past.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="self-end mt-4">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 opacity-70 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
            </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Sparen -->
        <a href="/sparen/" class="bg-neutral text-neutral-content rounded-xl p-6 pb-10 relative group hover:brightness-110 transition-all duration-300 min-h-[160px] flex flex-col justify-between" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="50">
            <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold italic mb-2">Sparen</h3>
                <p class="text-sm opacity-80">Wat je spaardoel ook is, wij helpen je verder.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="self-end mt-4">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 opacity-70 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
            </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Hypotheken -->
        <a href="/hypotheek/" class="bg-secondary text-secondary-content rounded-xl p-6 pb-10 relative group hover:brightness-110 transition-all duration-300 min-h-[160px] flex flex-col justify-between" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
            <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold italic mb-2">Hypotheken</h3>
                <p class="text-sm opacity-80">Verhuizen of verbouwen? Bereken snel wat je kunt lenen.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="self-end mt-4">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 opacity-70 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
            </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Verzekeren (full width) -->
        <a href="/verzekeren/" class="bg-neutral text-neutral-content rounded-xl p-6 pb-10 relative group hover:brightness-110 transition-all duration-300 min-h-[120px] lg:col-span-3 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between" data-aos="fade-up">
            <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold italic mb-2">Verzekeren</h3>
                <p class="text-sm opacity-80">Goed verzekerd zijn, helpt je om financieel gezond te blijven. Tot 12% pakketkorting op schadeverzekeringen.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4 md:mt-0 md:ml-8 flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 opacity-70 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
            </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Beleggen -->
        <a href="/beleggen/" class="bg-primary text-primary-content rounded-xl p-6 pb-10 relative group hover:brightness-110 transition-all duration-300 min-h-[160px] flex flex-col justify-between" data-aos="fade-up">
            <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold italic mb-2">Beleggen</h3>
                <p class="text-sm opacity-80">Bouw met ons vermogen op, voor nu en later.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="self-end mt-4">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 opacity-70 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
            </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Pensioen -->
        <a href="/pensioen/" class="bg-neutral text-neutral-content rounded-xl p-6 pb-10 relative group hover:brightness-110 transition-all duration-300 min-h-[160px] flex flex-col justify-between" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="50">
            <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold italic mb-2">Pensioen</h3>
                <p class="text-sm opacity-80">Straks net zo lekker leven als nu? Wij denken met je mee.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="self-end mt-4">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 opacity-70 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
            </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Lenen -->
        <a href="/lenen/" class="bg-neutral text-neutral-content rounded-xl p-6 pb-10 relative group hover:brightness-110 transition-all duration-300 min-h-[160px] flex flex-col justify-between" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
            <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold italic mb-2">Lenen</h3>
                <p class="text-sm opacity-80">Verbouwing, nieuwe auto of verduurzamen? Ontdek een persoonlijke lening bij je past.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="self-end mt-4">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 opacity-70 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
            </div>
        </a>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================== -->
<!-- SECTION: Wees alert (Fraud)    -->
<!-- ============================== -->
<section class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-6 py-12 md:py-16" data-aos="fade-up">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 md:gap-12">
        <div class="w-full md:w-5/12 flex-shrink-0">
            <img
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581579438747-104c53d7fbc4?w=600&h=450&fit=crop&crop=faces"
                alt="Persoon leest op de bank"
                class="rounded-lg w-full h-auto object-cover"
                loading="lazy"
                width="600"
                height="450"
            />
        </div>
        <div class="w-full md:w-7/12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold italic text-base-content mb-4">Wees alert</h2>
            <p class="text-base-content/70 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Steeds vaker raken organisaties betrokken bij datalekken. En zodra jouw
                gegevens op straat liggen, staan criminelen klaar om toe te slaan: via slimme
                phishingtrucs, een telefoontje van een 'bankmedewerker' die net echt klinkt of
                een ogenschijnlijk nette betalingsherinnering. Door bewust te blijven, houd je
                zelf de controle over je eigen veiligheid.
            </p>
            <a href="/en/veilig-online-bankieren/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary font-semibold hover:underline transition">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"></path></svg>
                Herken en voorkom fraude
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================== -->
<!-- SECTION: Rabo App Promotion    -->
<!-- ============================== -->
<section class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-6 py-8 md:py-12" data-aos="fade-up">
    <div class="bg-neutral text-neutral-content rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-stretch">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-8 md:p-12 lg:p-16 flex flex-col justify-center">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold italic mb-4">Bankzaken regel je met de Rabo App</h2>
                <p class="opacity-70 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
                    Spontaan uit eten vanavond? Check direct in de Rabo App hoe je ervoor staat.
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-success flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                        <span>Altijd en overal toegang tot je bankzaken</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-success flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                        <span>Handige tips en features</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-success flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                        <span>Uitgebreide online omgeving</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <div><a href="/betalen/rabo-app/" class="btn btn-primary">Lees meer</a></div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 flex justify-center items-end">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556742049-0cfed4f6a45d?w=500&h=600&fit=crop&crop=center" alt="Rabo App op smartphone" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" width="500" height="600"/>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================== -->
<!-- SECTION: Promo Card             -->
<!-- ============================== -->
<section class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-6 py-8 md:py-12" data-aos="fade-up">
    <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517457373958-b7bdd4587205?w=1200&h=500&fit=crop&crop=top" alt="Vrienden op een dakterras" class="w-full h-64 md:h-96 object-cover" loading="lazy" width="1200" height="500"/>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-neutral/90 via-neutral/50 to-transparent"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-8 md:p-12 text-white">
            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold italic mb-3">Open een betaalrekening en ontdek alle voordelen</h2>
            <p class="opacity-80 text-sm md:text-base max-w-xl mb-6">Naar de bios, een etentje met vrienden of sparen voor later? Jij bepaalt waar je je geld wel of niet aan uitgeeft. Ontdek de betaalrekening die bij je past.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                <a href="/betalen/betaalrekening/" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm md:btn-md">Bekijk betaalrekeningen</a>
                <a href="/betalen/creditcard/" class="btn btn-outline btn-sm md:btn-md text-white border-white hover:bg-white hover:text-neutral">Bekijk creditcards</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================== -->
<!-- SECTION: Magazine / Inzicht     -->
<!-- ============================== -->
<section class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-6 py-8 md:py-12" data-aos="fade-up">
    <div class="bg-neutral text-neutral-content rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-stretch">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-8 md:p-12 lg:p-16 flex flex-col justify-center">
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold italic mb-4">Financieel inzicht: tips en artikelen</h2>
                <p class="opacity-70 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
                    Van je eerste huis kopen tot duurzaam beleggen. Ontdek verhalen, tips en inzichten
                    die je helpen om slimmer met je geld om te gaan.
                </p>
                <div><a href="/en/eerste-huis-kopen-tips/" class="btn btn-primary">Lees de artikelen</a></div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600880292203-757bb62b4baf?w=600&h=500&fit=crop&crop=center" alt="Mensen in gesprek over financien" class="w-full h-full object-cover min-h-64" loading="lazy" width="600" height="500"/>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================== -->
<!-- SECTION: Heb je vragen?        -->
<!-- ============================== -->
<section class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-6 py-12 md:py-16" data-aos="fade-up">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold italic text-base-content mb-2">Heb je vragen?</h2>
    <p class="text-base-content/60 mb-8">Neem contact met ons op waar en wanneer je maar wilt.</p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <!-- Chat Card -->
        <div class="bg-primary/10 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden flex flex-col md:flex-row">
            <div class="p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col justify-end flex-1">
                <div class="bg-primary/20 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold italic text-base-content mb-1">Stel je vraag via chat</h3>
                <p class="text-base-content/60 text-sm mb-4">Direct antwoord van Robin, onze virtuele chat assistent.</p>
                <div><a href="/en/service-contact/" class="btn btn-neutral btn-sm">Start de chat</a></div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 flex-shrink-0">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1573497620053-ea5300f94f21?w=400&h=300&fit=crop&crop=faces" alt="Klantenservice medewerker" class="w-full h-48 md:h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" width="400" height="300"/>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Right column -->
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <a href="/en/service-contact/" class="bg-base-200 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 flex-1 hover:bg-base-300 transition-colors group">
                <div class="bg-base-300 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-primary/20 transition-colors">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-base-content/70" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-base font-bold italic text-base-content mb-1">Bel met een van onze medewerkers</h3>
                <p class="text-base-content/60 text-sm mb-3">Bereikbaar op werkdagen van 9.00 tot 17.00 uur.</p>
                <span class="btn btn-neutral btn-sm btn-outline">Bel ons</span>
            </a>
            <a href="/en/service-contact/" class="bg-base-200 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 flex-1 hover:bg-base-300 transition-colors group">
                <div class="bg-base-300 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-primary/20 transition-colors">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-base-content/70" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-base font-bold italic text-base-content mb-1">Online klantenservice</h3>
                <p class="text-base-content/60 text-sm mb-3">Vind het antwoord op onze website.</p>
                <span class="btn btn-neutral btn-sm btn-outline">Service & contact</span>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
